<div class="min-h-screen">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 pt-20">
    <header class="mb-12 text-center">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <pre class="text-sm inline-block glitch" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  ███████╗███████╗ ██████╗████████╗ ██████╗  ██████╗ ██╗     ███████╗ ║
║  ██╔════╝██╔════╝██╔════╝╚══██╔══╝██╔═══██╗██╔═══██╗██║     ██╔════╝ ║
║  ███████╗█████╗  ██║        ██║   ██║   ██║██║   ██║██║     ███████╗ ║
║  ╚════██║██╔══╝  ██║        ██║   ██║   ██║██║   ██║██║     ╚════██║ ║
║  ███████║███████╗╚██████╗   ██║   ╚██████╔╝╚██████╔╝███████╗███████║ ║
║  ╚══════╝╚══════╝ ╚═════╝   ╚═╝    ╚═════╝  ╚═════╝ ╚══════╝╚══════╝ ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
        </pre>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3 theme-header glitch" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">
        <span data-theme="hacker">[SECURITY TESTING FRAMEWORK]</span>
        <span data-theme="professional" style="display: none;">Security Testing Framework</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-family: var(--font-family);">
        <span data-theme="hacker">> Application & Product Security Testing Arsenal_</span>
        <span data-theme="professional" style="display: none;">Application & Product Security Testing Arsenal</span>
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary); font-family: var(--font-family);">
        <span class="animate-pulse" data-theme="hacker">█</span>
        <span data-theme="hacker">SYSTEM READY | <%= @categories.length %> CATEGORIES | <%= ToolRegistry.all.length %> TOOLS LOADED</span>
        <span data-theme="professional" style="display: none;"><%= @categories.length %> Categories | <%= ToolRegistry.all.length %> Tools Available</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <% if @categories.any? %>
      <% @categories.each do |category| %>
        <section class="mb-12">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="h-px flex-grow" style="background-color: var(--color-primary);"></div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold px-4 theme-header" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">
              <span data-theme="hacker">[ <%= category.upcase %> ]</span>
              <span data-theme="professional" style="display: none;"><%= category.titleize %></span>
            </h2>
            <div class="h-px flex-grow" style="background-color: var(--color-primary);"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <% @tools_by_category[category].each do |tool_class| %>
              <div class="theme-card scan-line">
                <div class="flex items-start mb-3">
                  <span class="text-2xl mr-2" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);" data-theme="hacker">▶</span>
                  <span class="text-2xl mr-2" style="color: var(--color-primary); display: none;" data-theme="professional">●</span>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold theme-header" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary);">
                    <%= tool_class.tool_name %>
                  </h3>
                </div>
                <p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-family: var(--font-family);">
                  <%= tool_class.tool_description %>
                </p>
                <div class="pt-4" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <%= link_to tool_path(tool_class.name.underscore.gsub('_tool', '')),
                      class: "inline-flex items-center text-sm font-bold transition-colors theme-link" do %>
                    <span class="mr-2" data-theme="hacker">></span>
                    <span class="underline" data-theme="hacker">EXECUTE TOOL</span>
                    <span class="underline" data-theme="professional" style="display: none;">Launch Tool</span>
                    <span class="ml-2 animate-pulse" data-theme="hacker">█</span>
                    <span class="ml-2" data-theme="professional" style="display: none;">→</span>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </section>
      <% end %>
    <% else %>
      <div class="text-center py-12">
        <div class="theme-card inline-block">
          <p class="text-xl mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary); font-family: var(--font-family);">
            <span data-theme="hacker">[!] NO TOOLS DETECTED</span>
            <span data-theme="professional" style="display: none;">No Tools Detected</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-tertiary); font-family: var(--font-family);">
            <span data-theme="hacker">Initialize tools in <code style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">/app/tools/</code></span>
            <span data-theme="professional" style="display: none;">Initialize tools in <code style="color: var(--color-primary);">/app/tools/</code></span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <footer class="mt-16 text-center pt-8" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
      <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-family: var(--font-family);">
        <span data-theme="hacker">[ POWERED BY RUBY ON RAILS <%= Rails.version %> ] | [ SECURE. TEST. REPEAT. ]</span>
        <span data-theme="professional" style="display: none;">Powered by Ruby on Rails <%= Rails.version %> • Secure. Test. Repeat.</span>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</div>
